ttp_template:
<group name="ip_address_age_mac_address_port">
Internet {{IP_ADDRESS | re("\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+")}} {{AGE}} {{MAC_ADDRESS | re("[0{{VLAN_ID | ORPHRASE}}9a-fA-F:.-]+")}} {{PORT | ORPHRASE}} - CP
</group>
<group name="ip_address_age_mac_address_port_vlan_id">
Internet {{IP_ADDRESS | re("\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+")}} {{AGE}} {{MAC_ADDRESS | re("[0-9a-fA-F:.-]+")}} {{PORT | ORPHRASE}} Vl {{VLAN_ID | ORPHRASE}} CP
</group>
<group name="ip_address_port_mac_address_vlan_id">
Internet {{IP_ADDRESS | re("\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+")}} {{PORT | ORPHRASE}} {{MAC_ADDRESS | re("[0{{AGE | re(".*\\w.*")}}9a-fA-F:.-]+")}} - Vl {{VLAN_ID | ORPHRASE}} CP
</group>
textfsm_template:
Value IP_ADDRESS ((?:[0-9]{1,3}\.){3}[0-9]{1,3})
Value MAC_ADDRESS ((?:[0-9a-fA-F]{2}\:){5}[0-9a-fA-F]{2})
Value PORT (\w{2} \d{1,2}\/\d{1,2}|\-)
Value AGE (\d+|\-)
Value VLAN_ID (\d+|\-)

Start
  ^Protocol\s+Address -> ARP

ARP
  ^Internet\s+${IP_ADDRESS}\s+${AGE}\s+${MAC_ADDRESS}\s+${PORT}\s+(Vl )?${VLAN_ID} -> Record
